item.title: #212 The Mutilator (1984)
item.description:
We waited about 7 years to cover this bad boy because Big Ed did not have enough relevance at the time. Since The Mutilator's inception, some big dude that puts mayonnaise in his hair appeared on 90 Day Fiance. That dude looks like my cat. Anyway, Big Ed is a hot topic like 3 years ago so we discussed the Mutilator. Hey Guys. It's a podcast!
